つまるとこ 人生ずっと地味
Basically, my life's always been drab.

247
00:20:28,432 --> 00:20:30,232
｢憎たらしい！｣｢痛々しい！｣
"How hateful! How pathetic!"

248
00:20:30,232 --> 00:20:31,732
無視出来ないのが一層
The way I can't ignore you makes it worse-

249
00:20:31,732 --> 00:20:33,232
腹立たしい 苛立たしい
How maddening, how vexing.

250
00:20:33,232 --> 00:20:35,332
そろそろ飽きた 自画自賛に (Look around!!)
I've had just about enough of blowing my own horn. (Look around!!)

251
00:20:35,332 --> 00:20:37,332
ライクの反対はアパシー ≒ 繋がれた証
The opposite of like is apathy ≈ proof that you're connected.

252
00:20:37,332 --> 00:20:39,132
切り離せない関係 逸らしてしまいたいわ
A relationship I can't cut off... I'd love to just look away from it.

253
00:20:39,132 --> 00:20:41,232
これは所謂 ヘイトスピーチ
This is what you'd call hate speech.

254
00:20:41,232 --> 00:20:44,232
匿名性の声明を生命に載せてんだ
We're slapping these anonymous declarations onto our very lives.

255
00:20:44,232 --> 00:20:47,332
鳴り止まないサイレン 近づく度に痙攣
We spasm every time those ceaseless sirens draw near.

256
00:20:47,332 --> 00:20:50,132
赤信号にずっと従順です。
We've obeyed red lights all this time.

257
00:20:50,132 --> 00:20:53,632
大体 アナタのコト アタシ ダイダイダイダイダイキライ
Point is, 'bout you, I absolutely--hate hate hate hate hate you.

258
00:20:53,632 --> 00:20:57,032
OMG 情けない 最早 バイバイバイバイバイしたい
OMG, how pathetic, I just wanna say--bye bye bye bye bye already.

259
00:20:57,032 --> 00:21:00,632
脳内も予測不能 故に 解解解解解は無い
Can't predict what's going on in that mind, and thus there's--no no no no no solution.

260
00:21:00,632 --> 00:21:04,232
どうだい？アタシのコト アナタ ダイダイダイダイダイキライになった？
How's it? 'Bout me, do you absolutely--hate hate hate hate me now?

261
00:21:04,232 --> 00:21:07,632
あァ 百害あって一利ナシ Nothing Not see
Ah, all pain and no gain, nothing, not see.

262
00:21:07,632 --> 00:21:11,132
もしタラレバ並べてもニコチンだし
It'd be like nicotine to think back on the what-ifs.

263
00:21:11,132 --> 00:21:14,632
I miss youって近付いた結末は凡ミス 凡ミス
Getting close because "I miss you," was a stupid mistake, mistake.

264
