センキュー 反面教師 後味 一生消えてくんないわ
Thanks for being a great bad example. You've left an aftertaste that won't ever disappear.

265
00:21:29,832 --> 00:21:33,432
よしよし いい子ね 笑顔振り撒き パラパラ いい子ね
Good, good, you're a good girl, smiling and spreading yourself around, good girl,

266
00:21:33,432 --> 00:21:34,932
だけど だけど その本性は？
but, but what's your true nature?

267
00:21:34,932 --> 00:21:37,032
善悪の区別も付かないの？笑 はぁ。
Can't you even tell right from wrong? LOL, sigh.

268
00:21:37,032 --> 00:21:40,432
減点方式で取り巻く環境に巻かれて
Winding myself up in an environment based on a point-deduction system,

269
00:21:40,432 --> 00:21:43,732
生涯、痛い！痛い！痛い！も聞かれないわ！って
My "It hurts! It hurts! It hurts!" won't be heard for a lifetime,

270
00:21:43,732 --> 00:21:47,032
当然の報いにクラっちゃった
I got hit by the inevitable retribution.

271
00:21:58,832 --> 00:22:00,632
人は鏡なんです
People are mirrors.

272
00:22:00,632 --> 00:22:02,432
実のところ 依存は両辺です
In truth, dependency is on both sides.

273
00:22:02,432 --> 00:22:06,032
シャットダウンしても付き纏う 己の弱さが不甲斐ない
Even if I shut down, I'm haunted by my own pathetic weakness.

274
00:22:06,032 --> 00:22:09,532
全部 全部 アンタのせいって 反吐が出るくらいに 止まんないわ
It's all, all your fault, I can't stop feeling... like I'm gonna hurl.

275
